styleUrlsData.data:
@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/utilities/text"

.button
  height: 38px
  display: inline-block
  color: $black
  text-align: center
  vertical-align: middle
  -webkit-user-select: none
  -moz-user-select: none
  -ms-user-select: none
  user-select: none
  background-color: transparent
  border: 1px solid transparent
  padding: 12px 16px
  border-radius: 4px
  transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out
  @extend .text-button

  &.button-disabled
    color: $gray-4 !important
    background-color: $gray-2 !important
    border-color: $gray-2 !important

  &:focus,
  &:active
    outline: none

  &.button-primary
    color: $white
    background-color: $primary
    border-color: $primary

    &:hover
      color: $white
      background-color: $dark-primary
      border-color: $dark-primary


  &.button-secondary
    color: $gray-6
    background-color: $gray-1
    border-color: $gray-1

    &:hover
      color: $gray-6
      background-color: $gray-2
      border-color: $gray-2

  &.button-outline
    color: $primary
    background-color: transparent
    border-color: $light-primary

    &:hover
      color: $primary
      background-color: $light-primary
      border-color: $light-primary

    &.button-disabled
      color: $gray-3 !important
      background-color: transparent !important
      border-color: $gray-3 !important

  &.button-ghost
    color: $primary
    background-color: transparent
    border-color: transparent

    &:hover
      color: $dark-primary
      background-color: transparent
      border-color: transparent

    &.button-disabled
      color: $gray-3 !important
      background-color: transparent !important
      border-color: transparent !important

components.templateData:
<button
  class="button"
  [class]="'button-' + appearance"
  [class.button-disabled]="disabled"
  [ngClass]="innerClass"
  [type]="behavior"
  [disabled]="disabled"
  [ngStyle]="inlineStyle"
  (click)="onClick($event)">
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</button>

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/mixins"
@import "src/sass/utilities/text"

.checkbox-container
  position: relative
  cursor: pointer
  display: inline-flex
  margin: 0
  @include non-selectable()

  .checkbox
    position: fixed
    left: 99999px
    opacity: 0

    &:checked ~ .checkbox-mark:after
      top: 2px
      left: 2px
      width: 10px
      height: 10px
      background-color: $primary

    &.checkbox-indeterminate ~ .checkbox-mark:after
      top: 5px
      left: 2px
      height: 4px
      width: 10px
      background-color: $primary

    &[disabled] ~ .checkbox-mark
      border: 1px solid $gray-2
      pointer-events: none
      cursor: default

    &[disabled] ~ .checkbox-content
      opacity: .5


  .checkbox-mark
    position: absolute
    top: 0
    left: 0
    z-index: 2
    height: 16px
    width: 16px
    border: 1px solid $gray-3
    background-color: $white
    border-radius: 2px

    &:after
      content: ""
      position: absolute
      top: 4px
      left: 4px
      width: 6px
      height: 6px
      background: white
      border: 0
      transition: top 0.3s, left 0.3s, width 0.3s, height 0.3s


  .checkbox-content
    display: inline-block
    padding-left: 24px
    min-height: 16px
    @extend .text-label

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/utilities/text"
@import "src/sass/mixins"

.input-label
  margin-bottom: 0

.input-basic
  background-color: $white
  padding: 12px 16px
  border: 1px solid $gray-3
  border-radius: 4px
  width: 100%
  color: $black
  height: 38px
  @extend .text-label

  @include placeholder
    color: $gray-4
    @extend .text-label

  &:-webkit-autofill
    -webkit-text-fill-color: $black

  &.input-error
    border-color: $danger
    color: $danger

    &:focus
      border-color: $danger
      color: $black

  &:disabled
    background-color: $gray-2
    border-color: $gray-3
    color: $gray-4

    [disabled]="inputDisabled"

@import "src/sass/variables"
@import "src/sass/utilities/text"
@import "src/sass/mixins"

.input-search-container
  position: relative
  margin: 0

  .input-search-icon

    left: 16px
    top: 13px

            [(ngModel)]="inputValue"

            (focus)="onFocus($event)">

    <app-icon class="input-search-icon"
              svgName="search"
              svgWidth="12px"></app-icon>
</label>
